channel.title: I'm Starting a Development Team! If you wanna join then read this
channel.description:
Hi guys, as everyone who codes even just a little bit knows that its very time comsuming. I've had lots of ideas that i haven't brought to life because. So now I'm going to start a development team. We will be creating anything like simple & complex programs, facebook apps, ipod/iphone apps, and Private Servers. To join, you will need to sign up on [url=http://enigmagaming.tk]my website[/url]. Once your signed in click the "Join the Dev Team" in the Nav Bar. Fill the request out with the layout below and rate your skills as Beginner,Apprentice,Intermediate,Advanced, or Expert. MS-Dos cmd - (SKILL RATING HERE) PHP - (SKILLRATING HERE) HTML - (SKILL RATING HERE) VB.NET - (SKILL RATING HERE) C# - (SKILL RATING HERE) C++ - (SKILL RATING HERE) Java - (SKILL RATING HERE)
Thank you all for your time and I hope you join. Happy Coding to all, grundyboy34
